Do We Need Local Developer Docs?
No. The kitchen sink export file + extraction script is a better approach because:

Retool docs describe the UI/API, not Transit JSON internals
Transit encoding is reverse-engineered from exports, not documented by Retool
The extraction script auto-generates accurate reference from real exports
Diffing docs wouldn't catch Transit format changes anyway
